             were indicted for <rs id="t17920113-36-off222" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17920113-36-off222" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17920113-36-off222" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17920113-36-cd223" type="crimeDate">23d of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920113-36-off222 t17920113-36-cd223"></join>, three hundred and seventy yards of printed callico, value 64 l. one hundred and sixty-eight yards, value 10 l. six yards ditto, value 18 s. three yards ditto, value 3 s. three yards ditto, value 3 s. five yards and a quarter of blue damask, value 35 l. and four damask tablecloths, the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17920113-36-victim434" type="victimName">
                           George 
                           Oakley
